      <title>《华尔街日报》称三星将把德州芯片支出增加至 440 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/samsung-to-hike-texas-chip-spending-to-44-billion-wsj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》援引知情人士消息称，三星电子公司计划将在德克萨斯州的投资增加至约 440 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/samsung-to-hike-texas-chip-spending-to-44-billion-wsj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 09:15:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通中信证券董事长再度洗牌辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/jpmorgan-china-securities-chairman-quits-in-another-reshuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通知情人士称，公司正在中国进行更多高层领导层变动，朴朴辞去其境内证券业务董事长一职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/jpmorgan-china-securities-chairman-quits-in-another-reshuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 09:01:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飞利浦警告呼吸机存在安全问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/philips-warns-of-faulty-ventilators-amid-mounting-safety-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皇家飞利浦公司警告称，其部分呼吸机可能会因突然断电而发生故障，这是困扰该公司的一系列产品安全问题中的最新一个。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/philips-warns-of-faulty-ventilators-amid-mounting-safety-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 08:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>iPhone 低迷后鸿海销量低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/hon-hai-sales-slump-offers-little-hope-for-iphone-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鸿海精密工业有限公司（Hon Hai Precision Industry Co.）受到 iPhone 销量下滑（尤其是在中国）的拖累，第一季度营收未能达到预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/hon-hai-sales-slump-offers-little-hope-for-iphone-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 07:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利电信签署 15 亿欧元过桥贷款用于再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/telecom-italia-signs-1-5-billion-bridge-loan-for-refinancing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Telecom Italia SpA 已签署 15 亿欧元（16 亿美元）过桥贷款，以满足其完成网络出售之前的再融资需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/telecom-italia-signs-1-5-billion-bridge-loan-for-refinancing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:59:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于电动汽车增长放缓，电池制造商 LG 能源利润暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/profit-at-battery-maker-lg-energy-plunges-amid-slower-ev-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LG Energy Solution Ltd. 的利润大幅下滑，原因是电动汽车增长放缓损害了该电池制造商的出货量和盈利能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/profit-at-battery-maker-lg-energy-plunges-amid-slower-ev-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:39:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
